Heathen Black Metal, hailing from Telemark in Norway!

Founded by Nasreten, Boghor and mr. Nielsen in 2007, after a couple of leaving and kicking of live and band members, some demo recordings and a few gigs, Visegard took a break from recruting members and live shows and left was mr. Nielsen and Nasreten.

After a couple of years, the recordings of a debut album was done, and it will be released winter 13/14!

In the process of the album creation, Skoll and mr. Wiersdalen joined with Visegard.
